long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Safnect Wallet is your gateway to the decentralized world, providing a non-custodial, decentralized crypto wallet experience powered by MPC technology. Safnect Wallet supports sending and receiving BTC, Fractal Bitcoin, ETH, and Runes seamlessly.

Safnect Wallet lets you stay in control with real-time access to your transaction history and status. Whether you’re on testnets or mainnets, Safnect has you covered. Your private key fragments are securely backed up in the cloud, and with MPC technology, your full private key only appears when authorized.

Explore the future of Web3 with Safnect Wallet, where security meets convenience—recover your wallet without the hassle of mnemonic phrases.
